STEN 1016/python3 tcp 0 0 127.0.0.1:631 0.0.0.0:* LISTEN - tcp6 0 0 ::1:631 :::* LISTEN - udp 0 0 0.0.0.0:161 0.0.0.0:* We can perform port forwarding using chisel Or check the list of processes and take a guess We see cups service Checking config shows that indeed port 631 belongs to cups If we curl we see the version is 1.6.1 If we check github post We see that we need to call cupsctl ErrorLog={FILE} And then curl 127.0.0.1:631/admin/log/error_log? So let&rsquo;s read shadow file It works, but it&rsquo;s not crackable

